├─ Mean time to repair (MTTR): 30 days (orbit replacement)
├─ Availability: 0.999 per satellite
└─ Redundancy: All critical systems 2N or N+1

Failure Modes and Effects Analysis (FMEA):
Critical items:
1. Quantum source: Triple redundancy with voting
2. Cryocooler: Dual redundant with cold redundancy
3. Pointing system: Dual star trackers, dual computers
4. Power system: Dual solar arrays, dual batteries
5. Communication: Dual transmitters, dual receivers

Orbital Spares: 10% of constellation (61 satellites) as active spares
```

